features: Floral Cocktail Napkins: This sunflower beverage napkins features assorted wildflower with green stems, leaves and butterflies on a white background. These napkins will definitely enhance your table and impress your guests. Napkins are 3-ply and measure 10” x 10” when unfolded and 5” x 5” when folded.
Durable And Strong: Napkins are made of high quality thick paper.These paper cocktail napkins are strong, durable, and thick so they are sure to hold up throughout drinks, dinner and dessert.

Decorative Party Napkins--Whether used for drink napkins, dessert napkins or appetizer napkins at the dining table, our sunflower and daisy flowers napkins will make your guests feel cared for and treated. This beautiful floral napkins also perfect for wedding, bridal shower, anniversaries, family gatherings, birthday dinners, tea parties, picnics, wine tasting, and baby shower decor.
Soft Material: The beverage napkins are made of quality paper material, which is safe and reliable, soft and absorbent, thick enough that not easy to tear, offering you a good using experience

More Time to Enjoy: Disposable paper reduces clean-up time so you can enjoy more time with friends and family. After the party just collect the tablecloths with all the garbage and throw it into the trash can. Presto! Cleanup completed!
body.description: Spring dinner napkins are a good choice for entertaining guests at spring parties, Sunday brunch, family banquets, buffets, barbecues, camping, etc.The spring sunflower decorative paper napkins can be given to your intimate family members and friends as wonderful housewarming gifts to express your love.
